🚀 TechBites TweakHub — Release Notes 🚀
🆕 What's New & Major Upgrades

⭐ Global Favorites System: Easily favorite your top tweaks! Plus, favorites are now synced so all users can see and share what's trending.

👤 Community Profile System: Achieve peak performance with 1-Click Optimizations. Create your own custom profiles, share them with the community, and climb the new Profile Rankings!

🛠️ Windows Fix (Troubleshooting Hub): A dedicated engine to detect, troubleshoot, and patch common Windows errors and bugs automatically.

🔄 One-Click Redo/Revert: Messed up a setting? The new dashboard Redo option lets you instantly revert your latest applied tweaks without hunting them down individually.

🖼️ Wallpaper Engine: Browse, choose, and apply custom Windows wallpapers seamlessly directly from the app.

📊 Network Usage Tracker: Live bandwidth tracking to monitor your system usage. (Under Development 🛠️)

🖱️ Cursor Customizer: Personalize your Windows cursor with custom themes. (Under Testing & Development 🧪)

⚙️ Reworks & Bug Fixes

📦 Software Manager Rework: Re-engineered the app installer backend to depend on Chocolatey instead of Winget to eliminate package deployment bugs.

🖼️ App Icon Fix: Resolved an issue where software application icons were failing to load or displaying incorrectly.

🎨 Customization Engine: Fixed various bugs affecting UI personalization and layout saving.

🛡️ Crash Fix: Patched critical system error code 7A82C7.

